reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Theses bottles were prefect!!
reviews.reviewText: The 4 bottles and the bag were excellent quality and worked so great for traveling. The 4 bottles fit enough shampoo, conditioner, body wash, and face wash for my two week trip. The silicone bottles did not leak while in the plane or during the trip. I was able to use these in my carry-on luggage. I had no problems through security either. The squeeze bottles were easy to use and I was worried when other reviews said too much product would come out, but I didn't have the problem. I just wish it came with a few of these silicone bottles that are half the size for smaller quantities. I got all the accessories just in case, but the other min jars with a screw lid are cheap plastic and would most likely leak. It would work for anything powder based tho, but I didn't have a use for them. The other little spray bottles look like they would work for hairspray or perfume, but I wasn't bringing that on my trip. The cleaner brushes would be useful too to clean out the bottles. Its a cute travel bag that allows you to bring your own products with you on the plane in a carry-on suitcase rather than having to use hotel stuff or buy products when you reach your destination and then have to leave them behind. It would also work for camping trips or a weekend road trip!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Worked as advertised. I had no issues with leakage. I put shower gel in one of larger containers (the squishy one) and hair gel and Vaseline in the smaller ones with the protective covers. I didn’t get an opportunity to use the spray bottles, but I would assume they work as expected. I had no issues with the bag size after adding contact lens solution, mouth wash, toothpaste & brush, etc.
